getMolecularWeights() now works. But SpeciesIndex() still does not
work. As you recommended, I deleted the underbar after SpeciesIndex in
pyrol_ftnlib.cpp (it was a stupid mistake..), but I still got the
following error message:

pyrol_ftnlib.cpp: In function &#39;interger speciesindex_ (char *, int)&#39;:
pyrol_ftnlib.cpp:321: no matching function for call to
&#39;Cantera::IdealGasMix::SpeciesIndex (string)&#39;

